Mustex and Stallex walk out of a cave near the ship.

Mustex: This is unbielivable, all the energon is stable.

Rhesus: I know I did a geologiacal scan of the area. That's how we 
know about the energon remember.  I also know about the underground 
river with an opening about 200 ft. long and 50 ft. wide.  And I also 
have the status of the engine.  Not so bad.  2 of the 3 thrusters will 
never run again, but I can turn them into automated cannons to defend 
this cave and the other one can be used to turn this shuttle into a 
submarine.  That river is wide enough to travel all the way out into 
the ocean.

Rhesus begins detaching the first of the thrusters/cannons.
